nodes.bodyText:
Without this change, executing ./checker/bin/javac -Alint=redundantNullComparison -processor nullness,regex  Repro.java would not warn about an unknown lint flag, but running ./checker/bin/javac -Alint=redundantNullComparison -processor nullness,guieffect Repro.java did produce a warning.
This now eagerly creates the active lint flags, always raising an error.
@smillst @mernst Does this sound good to you?

